## 2 Pipelines

### Pipeline A: ✦ New Content (from scratch)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    A["🎯 User enters topic\n(popup QInputDialog)"] --> B{Blueprint exists?}
    B -->|Yes| B1["Load _blueprint.json\n(skip research)"]
    B -->|No| C["Step 1: Research\n(Plan A: 3 Flash + 3 Pro)"]
    C --> D["Save _blueprint.json"]
    B1 --> E
    D --> E["Step 2: Framework Selection\n(AI ranking or user pick)"]
    E --> F["For each framework (1-2 versions):"]
    F --> G["_run_shared_fw_pipeline()"]
    G --> H["✦ Complete!"]
```

#### Step 1: Research (Plan A)
- **Function**: `research_blueprint_multicall()` in [rewriter.py](file:///f:/1.%20Edit%20Videos/8.AntiCode/2.Script_Split_Chapter/core/rewriter.py)
- **Phase 1**: 3 parallel Flash calls → 3 draft sections (Identity, Timeline, Themes)
- **Phase 2**: 3 parallel Pro calls → expand each draft (2-3x detail)
- **Output**: Merged blueprint dict → `_pipeline/_blueprint.json`
- **Skip logic**: If `_blueprint.json` exists, popup asks user → skip or re-research

#### Step 2: Framework Selection
- **Manual**: User picks from dropdown → single version
- **Auto**: AI ranks all frameworks → `_rankings.json`
  - v1 = top scorer (always)
  - v2 = 2nd scorer only if `score >= 8.5`

#### Steps 3-6: → Shared Pipeline (see below)

---

### Pipeline B: ▶ Rewrite (existing content)

> 2 sub-modes hoàn toàn khác nhau về pipeline

---

#### Mode: Narrative (8 steps) — dùng `_run_shared_fw_pipeline`

```
Step 1:    Concatenate all input chapter texts
Step 2:    Detect original framework (AI Flash)
Step 3:    Extract blueprint from existing content
Step 3.5:  Enrich blueprint  ← Google Search hoặc AI knowledge
Step 4:    AI framework ranking → auto-select 1-2 frameworks
           ├── Battle niche: must-have "Investigative Deep-Dive" + best remaining ≥ 8.5
           └── Default: top scorer + 2nd if ≥ 8.5
Step 5-8:  → _run_shared_fw_pipeline()  ← SHARED (outline → audit → write → review → patch → merge)
```

**Step 3.5: Enrich Blueprint** (Narrative only)
- **Function**: `enrich_blueprint_google(blueprint, gemini_keys, ...)`
- **Google Check ON**: Dùng Google Search fallback để bổ sung dữ liệu
- **Google Check OFF**: Dùng AI knowledge only
- **Output**: `_enrichment.json`, cập nhật `_blueprint.json`
- **Non-fatal**: Fail → continue pipeline

**Rewrite-specific extras:**
- `on_chapter_saved` callback → updates UI status per chapter
- `auto_patch` = checkbox value (not always True)
- `log_api` = actual logger (not suppressed)

---

#### Mode: Top/List Review (12 steps) — pipeline riêng, KHÔNG dùng shared

```
Step 1:    Concatenate texts
Step 2:    Detect original framework
Step 3:    Extract blueprint (product-focused)
Step 4:    Recommend framework (AI ranking)
Step 5:    Reality check blueprint (historical/spec verification)
Step 5a:   Spec verify via Google Search (firearms niche only)
Step 5b:   Price enrichment via Google Search (firearms niche only)
Step 5c:   Blueprint enrich (always runs — Google or AI)
Step 6:    Check blueprint completeness
Step 7:    Convert units (target country)
Step 8:    Create review outline
Step 9:    Audit outline
Step 10:   Write each chapter
Step 11:   Cross-chapter review + patch (uses review_cross_chapter)
Step 12:   Merge → FULL_SCRIPT.txt
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Top/List Review pipeline KHÔNG dùng `_run_shared_fw_pipeline()`** — nó có pipeline riêng inline
> vì có thêm nhiều bước đặc thù (reality check, spec verify, price enrich, unit convert)
> mà Narrative mode không cần.

