## Key Functions (in core/rewriter.py)

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `research_blueprint_multicall()` | Plan A research: 3 Flash → 3 Pro → merged blueprint |
| `recommend_framework()` | AI ranks frameworks by blueprint fit |
| `generate_renew_outline_v2()` | Create chapter outline from blueprint + framework |
| `audit_outline()` | AI reviews outline for structural issues |
| `write_from_blueprint()` | Write single chapter with context |
| `review_narrative_full()` | Cross-chapter review (Narrative mode) |
| `review_cross_chapter()` | Cross-chapter review (Top/List Review mode) |
| `patch_chapter_overlap()` | Fix single chapter based on review issue |

